===Adjective===
'''busy''' ([[busier]], [[busiest]])
# doing a great deal; having a lot of things to do
#:''It has been a '''busy''' day
# having a lot going on; [[complicated]] or [[intricate]]
#:''Flowers, stripes, and checkss in the same fabric make for a '''busy''' pattern.''

